    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Subscription Renewal Behavior Analysis\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Project Overview\\n\",\n",
    "    \"This notebook analyzes subscription customer behaviour to understand what factors relate to renewal, cancellation, and downgrade events. We study plan types, usage patterns, tenure, and engagement signals to identify at-risk subscribers.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Analyze subscription lifecycle events: renewal, cancellation, downgrade.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Identify behavioural patterns that precede churn vs renewal.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Segment subscribers by risk level using exploratory techniques.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Quantify the relationship between usage intensity and renewal probability.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Practice communicating subscription analytics insights.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Business / Research Problem\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Subscription businesses depend on renewals for revenue stability. Understanding why customers cancel or downgrade helps product and retention teams intervene proactively.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Why This Analysis Matters\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Acquiring a new subscriber costs 5-7× more than retaining an existing one. Even small improvements in renewal rate translate directly to revenue growth and lower customer acquisition costs.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"m002\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Dataset Overview\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Synthetic dataset of **5,000 subscribers** with:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `customer_id`, `signup_date`, `tenure_months`\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `plan` — Basic, Standard, Premium\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `monthly_price`, `payment_method`\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `logins_last_30d`, `features_used`, `support_tickets`\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `satisfaction_score` (1-10)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `outcome` — Renewed, Cancelled, Downgraded\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Dataset Source and License Notes\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Synthetically generated for educational purposes.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"m003\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Environment Setup\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
